name: Fancy Santa Claws! HO HO HO!
bio: Hi-ya! I'm Fancy Santa Claws! HO HO HO!. I'm a Aerobics Athlete  by day, and I like sleeping in fresh laundry by night. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. We're so fur-tunate to have found each other!
